column5: I talk to a guy in Kenora yesterday and he said boats are on the Lake of the woods. Any reports on Lac Seul or Red Lake? I heard 24" on Red Lake a week ago. Heat wave and rain came through Red Lake last week. I'd guess ice took a pounding.
Ice off of Vermilion Bay, Eagle Lake today. https://vermilionbaylodge.com/ice-out-may-3rd-2020/
Picture taken out my front window today, there is still ice on the lake, but it will be gone this week. No doubt Red Lake and Lac Seul still have ice also, but there could be some open spots.
Skywagon I like your view out your window helluva lot better than mine all's I see is cars going by and sirens all the time,I will have coffee tomorrow morn looking your view haha
